About this item

  • Certified HDMI 2.1 Cable: UGREEN 8K HDMI Cable features HDMI 2.1 Ultra High Speed certification to realize all HDMI 2.1 specialized functions, like 48Gbps ultra high speed transfer, eARC(Enhanced Audio Return Channel), dynamic HDR(high dynamic range), VRR (variable refresh rate), ALLM (auto low latency mode). Get this Certified HDMI 2.1 Cable to future-proof your 8K devices like gaming monitors of 240Hz/165Hz/144Hz/120Hz high refresh rate.
  • Improved Picture Quality: With 48Gbps explosive bandwidth, UGREEN 8K HDMI 2.1 Ultra High Speed Cable delivers more clear and sharper image and supports higher resolution and refresh rate up to 8K@60Hz, 4K@240Hz, 4K@165Hz, 4K@144Hz, 4K@120Hz, 1440P@144Hz.The 4K 120Hz HDMI Cable features VRR to reduce screen tearing, ALLM to eliminate lag, and dynamic HDR to realize life-like and vivid image. The Dolby Vision HDMI Cable is perfect for PS5/Xbox Series X supporting dynamic HDR.
  • Enhanced Sound Quality: The eARC feature of UGREEN HDMI 2.1 Dolby Atmos Cable not only simplifies the connections between TV and soundbar/AV receiver, but greatly expands compatibility uncompressed surround sound, including audio formats like DTS Master, DTS:X, Dolby TrueHD, and Dolby Atmos 3D surround sound. Get better surround sound experience with this high-quality HDMI eARC Soundbar Cable.
  • Sturdy &Solid: UGREEN 4K 240Hz HDMI 2.1 Cable is built to last. Made of high-quality materials(braided jacket, aluminium shell, nickel-plated plug), the PS5 HDMI 2.1 Cable resists more wear and tear, and provides excellent signal protection. 4-Layer solid shielding provides excellent protection to signal and offer crystal picture and clear sound.
  • Universal Fit: UGREEN 8K HDMI HDR HDCP 2.3 Cable fits snugly to devices of full-size HDMI 2.1/2.0/1.4/1.3 port, including PS5 Pro/PS5 Slim/PS4/PS3, Xbox Series X/S/One/360, NS switch 2/1/OLED dock, laptop, PC, computer, MacBook, iMac, DVD player, Blu-ray player, streaming TV box, video capture card, GPU, Fire TV, soundbar, HDTV, 8K/4K/1440P gaming monitor, AV receiver, projector, speaker, etc.

    Why Choose UGREEN 8K HDMI 2.1 Cable?

    Previous page

    1. See clearly and play more smooth

    2. 3D Ready, feel at the scene

    4. See clearly and get more details

    Next page

    8K HDMI 2.1 Cable Certified with 48Gbps Ultra High Speed, Dynamic HDR, eARC, VRR

    Future-proofing Certified 8K HDMI 2.1 Cable

    UGREEN 8K HDMI Cable features HDMI 2.1 Ultra High Speed Certification and delivers maxmium 48Gbps transfer rate. Explosive bandwidth supports higher resolution and refresh rate up to 10K@60Hz, 8K@60Hz, 4K@240Hz, 4K@165Hz, 4K@144Hz, 4K@120Hz, 1440P@144Hz and 1080P@240Hz. Get more clear and sharper pictures with UGREEN Certified HDMI 2.1 Cable. Ideal for PS5, Xbox Series X/S, gaming monitor like Odyssey OLED G9/Odyssey Neo G9.

    Dynamic HDR, More Realistic Picture

    The 4K 120Hz HDMI 2.1 Cable supports dynamic HDR, including HDR10+ & Dolby Vision, to deliver a frame-by-frame level of detail. See every detail and get a more realistic image that feels like it is jumping off the screen.

    VRR And ALLM Ready, Smoother Gaming

    UGREEN Ultra High Speed HDMI 2.1 Cable is built for game consoles with HDMI 2.1 ports, like PS5 Pro/PS5/Xbox Series S/Series X. The 4K 144Hz HDMI 2.1 Cable has advanced features like VRR (variable refresh rate) to reduce screen tearing and ALLM (auto low latency mode) to reduce lag. Always win the games with this 8K HDMI 2.1 Cable.

    HDMI 2.1 eARC, Full-Resolution Audio

    With Enhanced Audio Return Channel (eARC), the HDMI HDR Dolby Atmos Cable not only simplifies the connections between your TV and soundbars/AV receivers, but also greatly improves sound quality. The eARC HDMI 2.1 Cable supports uncompressed surround sound, including audio formats like DTS Master, DTS:X, Dolby TrueHD, and Dolby Atmos 3D surround sound.

    Warm Reminder: 1/ The 8K HDMI 2.1 Cable is available in 0.5M/1M/2M/3M/5M/10M. 2/ To realize HDMI 2.1 features like 4K@240Hz/144Hz/120Hz, eARC function and VRR, your devices feature standard HDMI 2.1 or 2.2 ports. 3/ If screen is black or green, try to unplug the HDMI 2.1 cables from your devices and then replug, or restart the devices. 4/ Set the resolution and refresh rate to a compatible one for your devices. And select the matched HDMI port as video signal source on your TV or monitor.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    5 out of 5 stars
    High quality and solid cable works perfectly
    I previously got a "slim and thin" HDMI 2.1 cable from UGREEN which worked perfectly, both for direct connection just to a 4K player, and as the main eARC connection to my receiver. I decided to get another cable for the main eARC connection to my receiver so I went for this one that is a bit 'chunkier' and more substantial. I'm not sure really if it's necessary since the "slim and thin" one works just fine for this, but for the main system 'pipe' I decided to go with the thicker one. Possibly the extra thickness is just padding or shielding. The attached pictures show the difference. The end of this one is about twice the size of the "slim and thin" one while the cable is maybe half as thick again. But the end is not too big to be manageable and plugs easily into my receiver and TV with a solid feeling connection with little play. The braided cable is not too stiff either. It worked perfectly as soon as I fired up my system with no delays or image issues. In the packaging the cable came in a re-sealable pack and inside this was fully shrink-wrapped in quite thick plastic. So it was double-packaged basically. This shows good attention to detail. It seems very high quality and well made. I feel confident this cable is going to keep me well connected and future proof for a good while. Highly recommended.
